\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYCm0Jf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYCm0Jf.jpg&h=40377c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7ZpdX5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7ZpdX5.png&h=984be9d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkbOFNr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkbOFNr.png&h=6c0725b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsteve寫話捐錢都好信，到時唔捐邊又好似果80萬咁落咗格，好似佢啲卡game咁成年幾都唔發貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且佢都係寫捐612呢d大路，不如自己捐咗佢算<br />\n 味見過邊間黃店咁大口氣用手足價三個字，龍門渣哥做咁多野都唔叫自己良店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要同出邊個價冇分別咁咪即係普通做生意，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用咩鬼手足價<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">水貨化妝品都當黃店咁金鋪都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊度黃啊企開啲啊</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勁多打手即刻咬我話比次機會，啲檔主好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想講咁多黃年宵唔一定要去呢個，唔該大家唔好貪方便，去個藍尸搞既同去咗個政府年宵冇分，政府年宵裏面啲檔主都可以好黃，你會唔會比次機會？</span></span>"},{"pid":"19c7a61590c8ca10285020265f57c1b9802118e5","tid":1828291,"uid":118325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T18:57:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"773b3ef23d7cfd07149660cdbc95fd52a08675bd","tid":1828291,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T19:00:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e5526953f502b4a87851b439b6ae779e0fb85eb5","tid":1828291,"uid":297453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T19:04:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2122e70ba2c29569f83604476d605a09edcfdd7b","tid":1828291,"uid":147464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T19:11:48.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}